Package org.jboss.windup.rules.apps.java.model

Interface JavaClassModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BelongsToProject, com.syncleus.ferma.ElementFrame, HasApplications, HasProject, com.syncleus.ferma.VertexFrame, WindupFrame<org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Vertex>, WindupVertexFrame
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AmbiguousJavaClassModel, PhantomJavaClassModel
    public interface JavaClassModel
extends WindupVertexFrame, BelongsToProject, HasApplications, HasProject
    Represents a JavaClass, either from a .class file or a .java source file.
